        <button class="node-btn rounded-4xl p-5 text-left" onclick="openModal('m6')">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-2xl bg-amber-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-black">06</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-500 font-extrabold">Etapas</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight text-slate-950 leading-tight">6 frentes iniciales</div>
          <div class="mt-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">El arranque se organiza en seis frentes de avance.</div>
        </button>

        <button class="node-btn rounded-4xl p-5 text-left" onclick="openModal('m7')">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-black">07</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-500 font-extrabold">Tiempo</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight text-slate-950 leading-tight">Secuencia definida · activación progresiva</div>
          <div class="mt-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Avance por frentes y validaciones internas.</div>
        </button>

        <button class="node-btn rounded-4xl p-5 text-left" onclick="openModal('m8')">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-2xl bg-cyan-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-black">08</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-500 font-extrabold">Minivictorias</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight text-slate-950 leading-tight">Resultado por etapa</div>
          <div class="mt-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Cada frente deja una ganancia concreta y visible.</div>
        </button>

        <button class="node-btn rounded-4xl p-5 text-left" onclick="openModal('m9')">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-2xl bg-teal-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-black">09</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-500 font-extrabold">Avance</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight text-slate-950 leading-tight">Movimiento desde etapa 1</div>
          <div class="mt-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">No se queda en diagnóstico; empieza a activarse.</div>
        </button>

        <button class="node-btn rounded-4xl p-5 text-left" onclick="openModal('m10')">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-2xl bg-blue-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-black">10</div>
